latestIgtvVideos.caption:

latestIgtvVideos.title: Morning routine.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
How you start your day determines how your entire day is going to be, these few minutes in the morning really helps me prepare myself for the day and reflect upon my learnings from the past. 
Right after I wake up I hop into the shower and let the cold water relax my body, I prefer a gentle scrub to remove my dead skin and a mild body wash. Right after my shower I like to clean my face with a cleanser and peel off mask which helps me look young and fresh. I've been using @manarden from quite some time now and it has surely lived up to my expectations. Do check their website for amazing offers www.manarden.com
And don't forget to follow @manarden

#mengroomingredefined #manarden

The poem ozymandias in the video  leaves a message that wealth, power and position don’t last forever. So they should be used for the welfare of mankind and should not be misused. Time is ultimate leveler. One must realise that respect is never demanded it is earned. Real power is winning the hearts and not in ruling in the weak and the needy. Time conquers all, so winning the hearts of the people is real victory.
So, live for yourself and make sure you take care of your body and mind, that's where your real happiness lies.

Music: Delibes: Lakmé / Act 1 - "Viens, Mallika, ... Dôme épais" by Dame Joan Sutherland, Jane Berbié, Orchestre National de l'Opéra de Monte-Carlo, Richard Bonynge
